•   inv.0 ≡ z = 0 ∧ y = 1 ∧ x = 0

⊩   inv.0

≡   Definition of inv

    ( n, z, y, x : n ≥ 0 : z = s.n ∧ y = f.(n+1) ∧ x = f.n ).0

≡   λ comp

    •   0 ≥ 0
    
    z = s.0 ∧ y = f.(0+1) ∧ x = f.0

≡   Arithmetic

    z = s.0 ∧ y = f.1 ∧ x = f.0

≡   Theory [1]; Definition of f

    z = 0 ∧ y = 1 ∧ x = 0

■